  • FICE Federal ID number
  • X College name
  • State
  • PPIND Public/private indicator (public=1, private=2)
  • AVRMATH Average Math SAT score
  • AVRVERB Average Verbal SAT score
  • AVRCOMB Average Combined SAT score
  • AVR_ACT Average ACT score
  • MATH_1 / MATH_3 First / Third quartile - Math SAT
  • VERB_1 / VERB_3 First / Third quartile - Verbal SAT
  • ACT_1 / ACT_3 First / Third quartile - ACT
  • APP_REC Number of applications received
  • APP_ACC Number of applicants accepted
  • NEW_STUD Number of new students enrolled
  • NEW_10 / NEW_25 Pct. new students from top 10% / 25% of H.S. class
  • FULLTIME / PARTTIME Number of fulltime / parttime undergraduates
  • IN_STATE In-state tuition
  • OUT_STATE Out-of-state tuition
  • R_B_COST Room and board costs
  • ROOM Room costs
  • BOARD Board costs
  • ADD_FEE Additional fees
  • BOOK Estimated book costs
  • PERSONAL Estimated personal spending
  • PH_D Pct. of faculty with Ph.D.s
  • TERM_D Pct. of faculty with terminal degree
  • SF_RATIO Student/faculty ratio
  • DONATE Pct.alumni who donate
  • INSTRUCT Instructional expenditure per student
  • GRADUAT Graduation rate
  • SAL_ salaries
  • COMP_ average compensation
  • NUM_ number of people

p <- ncol(uni) - 2

dudi.pca. PCA .

pca <- dudi.pca(uni[,3:ncol(uni)], scannf = FALSE, nf = p)

EL <- sapply(1:(p), function(i){
  1/(p) * sum(1/(i:(p)))
}) 

plot(pca$eig/(p),  main = "Eigenvalues",  ylab = "Eigenvalue/sum(eigenvalues)", xlab = "Eigenvalue number", type = "b", ylim = c(0,0.5))
lines(EL, col = "red")
text(pca$eig/p, labels =  round(pca$eig/(p), digits = 2), cex= 0.5, pos=3)

, barplot :

r.sqr <- apply(pca$co[,1:2],1, function(x){
  sum(x^2)
})
r.sqr <- sort(r.sqr)
barplot(r.sqr, ylab = "R2", xlab = "", main = "R2(Xi, span{V1, V2})", ylim = c(0,1), names.arg = names(r.sqr), las = 2, cex.names = 0.7)

e <- diag(nrow = p)
plot(pca$li[,1]/sqrt(pca$eig[1]), pca$li[,2]/sqrt(pca$eig[2]), pch = 19, cex = 1, lty = "solid", lwd = 2, xlab = "PC1", ylab = "PC2", main = "PC1 vs PC2 (grouped by PPIND)", col = uni$PPIND,  ylim = c(-4,4), xlim = c(-4,4) )
legend('topright',legend = unique(uni$PPIND),col=1:length(uni$PPIND),pch=1)

text(pca$li[,1]/sqrt(pca$eig[1]), pca$li[,2]/sqrt(pca$eig[2]), labels = rownames(pca$li), cex= 0.7, pos=3)
